.getName())\n                .isEqualTo(\"org.apache.commons.httpclient.cookie.CookieSpec\");\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void parsesValidatesMatchesAndFormatsBrowserCompatibleCookie() throws Exception {"},{"oldText":"\n    private static CookieSpecBaseClassLoader newCookieSpecBaseClassLoader() {\n        URL location = CookieSpecBase.class.getProtectionDomain().getCodeSource().getLocation();\n        return new CookieSpecBaseClassLoader(new URL[] {location},\n                CookieSpecBaseTest.class.getClassLoader());\n    }\n\n    private static final class CookieSpecBaseClassLoader extends URLClassLoader {\n        private CookieSpecBaseClassLoader(URL[] urls, ClassLoader parent) {\n            super(urls, parent);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        protected Class<?> loadClass(String name, boolean resolve) throws ClassNotFoundException {\n            synchronized (getClassLoadingLock(name)) {\n                if (COOKIE_SPEC_BASE_CLASS_NAME.equals(name)) {\n                    Class<?> loadedClass = findLoadedClass(name);\n                    if (loadedClass == null) {\n                        loadedClass = findClass(name);\n                    }\n                    if (resolve) {\n                        resolveClass(loadedClass);\n                    }\n                    return loadedClass;\n                }\n                return super.loadClass(name, resolve);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}","newText":"\n}"}]}
